{"tid":1635722,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有樣嘢我真係唔撚明 全部人入嚟答我","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:54:06.000Z","uid":83557,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba9f24f12e7d0f5664fac1c76843232e8ec60ff","tid":1635722,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"今晚開花 個目標係咪想幫聽日被大三罷？<br />\n如果係<br />\n你搞黨鐵站係好合理<br />\n但係有樣野我就唔撚明喇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點撚解唔搞埋交通燈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你話會搞到自己人 咁其實好多嘢都會搞到自己人<br />\n遊行 裝修 火魔法 全部都會搞到自己人 係咪以後唔搞？<br />\n好老實 一個正常司機見到盞交通燈熄咗<br />\n咁就一定會慢駛啦 咁又點樣發生交通意外呢<br />\n如果你淨係搞黨鐵唔搞路面 邊有藉口比香港人唔返工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係要全港交通大癱瘓呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然你都可以話自發罷工 你覺得香港人可以嘅咪繼續呃自己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚開花好似少咗好多人 可能大家都攰 可以休息 但唔好俾團火熄 <br />\n<br />\n香港人 反抗！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n以上內容純屬虛構 與本人無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847d491e60a15b2631597016475bfdbf06b0f6d3","tid":1635722,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"d67f35ac1842ec2f6076f303932b17b7c4fe6fc1","tid":1635722,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"089292832692bbe145de2b310fb4f5df463ebf19","tid":1635722,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"d5fab81632fda0d3dc28a0db6a482e7b0143786a","tid":1635722,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"推 4/10"},{"pid":"8fc2ccbcb8689585dbae566ff9c70a48cbf9dc92","tid